OL,3,CPope puts 'God's architect' Antoni
OL,4,CGaudi on the path to sainthood
OL,6,FThe Vatican announced on Monday that
OL,7,FAntoni Gaudi, long nicknamed "God's
OL,8,Farchitect", is on the path to
OL,9,Fsainthood.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the Vatican
OL,12,Facknowledged Gaudi's "heroic virtues"
OL,13,Fas explanation for the Pope's decision
OL,14,Fto make him venerable.
OL,16,FThe Catalan architect is best known
OL,17,Ffor designing Barcelona's iconic
OL,18,FSagrada Familia, which is set to be
OL,19,Fcompleted in 2026, more than 140 years
OL,20,Fafter construction began.
