OL,3,CPope puts 'God's architect' Antoni
OL,4,CGaudi on the path to sainthood
OL,6,FGaudi's legacy is tied to Catholicism
OL,7,Fand he envisioned his Basilica to be
OL,8,F"a Bible in stone" with 18 huge,
OL,9,Fspindle-shaped towers, each
OL,10,Fsymbolizing a different biblical
OL,11,Ffigure ` the 12 apostles, the four
OL,12,Fevangelists, the Virgin Mary and Jesus.
OL,14,FPope Francis' declaration, which comes
OL,15,Fnearly a centaury after the architects
OL,16,Fdeath, is one of the first steps in
OL,17,Fthe long and complex process towards
OL,18,Fbecoming a saint.
