OL,3,CPope puts 'God's architect' Antoni
OL,4,CGaudi on the path to sainthood
OL,6,FTo become a saint, a candidate
OL,7,Fnormally needs two miracles to be
OL,8,Fattributed to them, which is examined
OL,9,Fby theologians and then ultimately the
OL,10,Fdecision to canonise someone is made
OL,11,Fby the Pope.
OL,13,FVery few artists become saints and no
OL,14,Farchitect, in the modern understanding
OL,15,Fof the profession, has ever been
OL,16,Fcanonised so finding those miracles
OL,17,Fwill be the next step in this process.
