OL,3,CPope puts 'God's architect' Antoni
OL,4,CGaudi on the path to sainthood
OL,6,FFor decades, groups like the
OL,7,FAssociation for the Beatification of
OL,8,FAntoni Gaudi have been campaigning for
OL,9,Fhis recognition by the Catholic Church.
OL,11,FThe Archbishop of Barcelona took up
OL,12,Fthe cause in 2023 and submitted the
OL,13,F"positio", or key argument, for
OL,14,FGaudi's beatification to the Vatican.
OL,16,FAntoni Gaudi was struck by a tram and
OL,17,Fdied in 1926 when only 10%-15% of the
OL,18,FBasilica had been built.
